Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "ema" in different forms and positions:

1. *Ema* je moja omiljena pesma. (*Ema* is my favorite song.) 
2. Sinoć sam gledao *Emin* novi film. (Last night I watched *Emin's* new movie.)
3. Moram da kupim knjigu o *emi*. (I need to buy a book about *EMI*.)
4. *Emi* se dopada taj momak. (*Emi* likes that guy.)
5. *Ema* je rekla da će doći kasnije. (*Ema* said she'll come later.)
6. U *eminom* stanu ima puno knjiga. (There are a lot of books in *Emin's* apartment.)
7. *Emin* glas je prelep. (*Emin's* voice is beautiful.)
8. *Emu* se svidela ta pesma. (He liked that song.)
9. Danas se održava *ema* konferencija. (The *EMA* conference is being held today.)

I hope these examples help!